/* ------------------------------------------------------------------ */
/*  Database types                                                     */
/*                                                                     */
/*  The canonical `Database` type and all Row / Insert / Update /      */
/*  Enum helpers are AUTO-GENERATED by `supabase gen types`.           */
/*                                                                     */
/*  Regenerate:  npx supabase gen types typescript --local \           */
/*               | Out-File -Encoding utf8 src/lib/types/database.generated.ts */
/*                                                                     */
/*  This file provides:                                                */
/*    1. Re-exports of generated helpers (Database, Tables, etc.)      */
/*    2. Short convenience aliases (OrderRow, ProductRow, …)           */
/*    3. JSONB shape types for casting (AddressJson, PlanFeaturesJson) */
/*    4. Enriched/join types not in the DB (ReviewWithUser, etc.)      */
/* ------------------------------------------------------------------ */

